(52, 'USB 3.1 Kingston Zodiac Puppy 2018 32GB Limited Edition', 30, 50, 'zodiac-puppy-2018-01.jpg,zodiac-puppy-2018-02.jpg,zodiac-puppy-2018-07.jpg', 2, 5, '<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Product type: USB\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Capacity: 32 GB\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Connection standards: USB 3.1, 3.0, 2.0\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Material: Metal\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Read speed: 100 MB / s\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Warranty: 5 years\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<blockquote>\r\n<p>USB 3.1 Kingston Zodiac Puppy 2018 32GB</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Limited version</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>USB 3.1 Kingston Zodiac Puppy 2018 32GB</strong> is a special limited edition for the 2018 Tet holiday in Asian markets. With a unique design the dog creates a lucky symbol at the beginning of the new year. The product is contained in a very luxurious metal box, suitable for use as a gift or souvenir. With limited production, this is the USB you need to own right in the Tet Tuat Tet holiday. The 2018 USB 3.1 Kingston Zodiac Puppy has a high-speed 3.1 interface, which ensures the performance and speed required for a high-end USB. Also compatible with USB 3.0, 2.0, 1.1 ports. USB 3.1 is the successor to the USB 3.0 standard, which can be identified by the green connection port. USB 3.1 doubles the transfer rate to 10Gbps, which is fully compatible with older devices. Kingston Zodiac Puppy USB 3.1 2018 is backed by a 5-year warranty.</p>\r\n', 1, 32),
(53, 'USB 3.1 Samsung BAR Plus 32GB MUF-32BE', 19, 29, 'bar-plus-silver-01.jpg,muf-32be-01.jpg,muf-32be-02.jpg', 2, 3, '<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Product type: USB 3.1\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Capacity: 32 GB\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Material: Metal\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Read speed: 150 MB / s\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Warranty: 2 years\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h2>Speed in Style</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>A modern take on a classic. The next generation Bar Plus elevates the flash drive to an everyday essential, offering impressive speeds in a striking design. Fits in your hand, a pure minimalism that cleverly blends style, speed, and reliability</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Move Files in a Flash&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Get your time back. Fast and convenient read speeds up to 300 MB/s&sup1; with the latest USB 3.1 standard gives you more time to work, play, watch, and create. Send a 3GB 4K UHD video file from your Bar Plus to your PC in just 10 seconds&sup2;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&sup1;Up to 300 MB/s for 256/128GB models; Up to 200 MB/s for 64/32GB models.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&sup2;Minimum of 10 secs for 256/128GB models; Minimum of 14 secs for 64/32GB models (tested with combination of Asus Z370-G, Intel i7-8700K@3.70GHz, 8GB DDR4 and Windows 10 Enterprise 64bit).</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Rugged Refinement</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>As rugged as it is stylish. The sturdy metal body keeps your data safe and intact, and the integrated key ring prevents accidental misplacement or loss. The Bar Plus is the ideal combination of stunning design and worry-free durability.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Tough &amp; Trusted</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Files stay secure, anywhere you go. Samsung&#39;s leadership in flash memory makes the Bar Plus a trustworthy drive to store your valuable data. It works through it all with a waterproof&sup1;, shock-proof&sup2;, temperature-proof&sup3;, magnet-proof&#8308;, and X-ray-proof&#8309; body, all backed by a 5-year limited warranty&#8310;.</p>\r\n', 1, 32),
