(55, 'USB 3.1 SanDisk Ultra Fit CZ430 16GB', 8, 30, 'cz430-01.jpg,cz430-02.jpg,cz430-16gb.jpg', 2, 2, '<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Product type: USB 3.1\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Capacity: 16 GB\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Plastic material\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Read speed: 135 MB / s\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Warranty: 5 years\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p><strong>USB 3.1 Sandisk Ultra Fit CZ430</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Move, store and share files ten times faster</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>With read speeds up to 130 MB / s 10 times faster than USB 2.0, the SanDisk Ultra Fit USB 3.1 CZ430 Flash Drive allows you to move, store and share your favorite information quickly fast. With up to 256GB capacity, maximize the storage space for your device quickly or move files between laptops, tablets, game consoles, TVs, sound systems Car bar, or other USB device. You can even transfer a full length movie in just 40 seconds. In addition, SanDisk Ultra Fit USB 3.1 CZ430 USB Flash Drive is backward compatible with USB 2.0 port for you to use with any device that supports USB port</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Compact, Plug-and-Stay design and extremely large storage capacity</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>SanDisk Ultra Fit USB 3.1 CZ430 USB Flash Drive is designed to be extremely small, fits into the device&#39;s USB port and is designed to be plugged in continuously without removing it, so you don&#39;t have to worry about being fall or crack. And with a capacity of up to 256GB, you will have plenty of space for all photos, videos, music, and games.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>*** Because of its small size, the operating temperature can be higher than the large size models.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Bandwidth 3.1 extremely high speed</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>SanDisk Ultra Fit USB 3.1 CZ430 USB Flash Drive is equipped with ultra-wide 3.1 bandwidth for ultra-fast data transfer speeds of up to 130MB / s. 15 times more than USB 2.0 standard.</p>\r\n', 1, 16),
