(65, 'SSD Kingston UV500 3D-NAND SATA III 120GB SUV500120G', 30, 50, 'suv500-2-5-inches-01.jpg,suv500-2-5-inches-120gb.jpg', 3, 5, '<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Standard SSD: 2.5 inches\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Reading speed: 560 MB / s\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Write speed: 530 MB / s\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Warranty: 3 years\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p><strong>Kingston UV500 Series SSD hard drive</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Enjoy new power in your computer system</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kingston&#39;s Kingston UV500 Series SSD is equipped with Marvell four-channel control chip with amazing speed and higher performance than a mechanical HDD hard drive.&nbsp;Dramatically improve the responsiveness of the current system and 10 times faster than a 7200RPM hard drive.&nbsp;With extremely high reliability and durability, the Kingston UV500 Series SSD hard drive uses 3D-NAND flash memory with excellent anti-shock and anti-vibration capabilities and is less likely to damage than a regular HDD hard drive.&nbsp;Suitable for many portable devices such as Laptops, Macbooks, etc. The Kingston UV500 Series SSD hard drives come in a variety of capacities ranging from 120GB to 960GB, giving you a wide range of options to suit your needs. About storage space for all files, applications, videos, photos and other important documents.&nbsp;In addition,</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Marvell control chip</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Kingston UV500 Series SSD is equipped with a 4-channel Marvell controller with impressive speed for both compressed and uncompressed data.&nbsp;It has an optimized processor for super high performance and durability.</p>\r\n', 1, 120),
(67, 'SSD Samsung 860 Evo 250GB 2.5-Inch SATA III MZ-76E250BW', 50, 60, '860-evo-2-5-inch-01-d0b3ac57-309c-4112-9430-d440ad904689.jpg,860-evo-2-5-inch-03.jpg,860-evo-2-5-inch-04.jpg', 3, 3, '<p>\r\n	Standard SSD: 2.5 inches<br>\r\n	Read speed: 550 MB / s<br>\r\n	Write speed: 520 MB / s<br>\r\n	Warranty: 5 years\r\n</p>\r\n', '<h2><strong>Boosted endurance</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Safely store and render large sized 4K videos and 3D data used by the latest applications, up to 8x higher TBW (Terabytes Written)* than the previous 850 EVO. The latest V-NAND technology gives you up to 2,400 TBW, or is backed by a 5-year limited warranty.*</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Smart compatibility</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Benefit from faster, more fluid communication with your host system. The refined ECC* algorithm and a new MJX controller generate higher speeds, and the improved queued trim enhances Linux compatibility. Our advanced engineering makes the 860 EVO more compatible with your computing system.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>Multi form factors</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Whatever size your computer needs, there is an 860 EVO for you. Choose among the 2.5-inch size for desktop PCs and laptops, and the SATA-based M.2 (2280) or the mSATA for ultra-slim computing devices.</p>\r\n', 1, 250),
(68, 'SSD Samsung 860 Evo 250GB M.2 2280 SATA III MZ-N6E250BW', 49, 25, '860-evo-m-2-250gb-01.jpg,860-evo-m-2-250gb-03.jpg,860-evo-m-2-250gb-04.jpg', 3, 1, '<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		SSD standard: M.2 2280 SATA III\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Read speed: 550 MB / s\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Recording speed: 520 MB / s\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Warranty 5 years 1 exchange 1.\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p><strong>Hard drive&nbsp;Samsung SSD 860 line drives to be upgraded from the current 850 EVO reputation and best-selling worldwide, is the best choice for gamers in both price and performance is confirmed and detailed evaluation Details by the world&#39;s leading technology magazines such as Cnet, thessdreview, the PC World.&nbsp;TweakTown ..</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Samsung 64-Layer 3D V-NAND Technology</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Samsung Technology 64-Samsung&#39;s 3D Layer V-NAND is a breakthrough in Flash memory architecture by increasing the density, performance, and limit of endurance of conventional flat NAND architecture.&nbsp;The Samsung 3D V-NAND technology arranges 64 layers of longitudinal Cell cells which increases the Cell density higher and performs twice as well as the 32-Layer technology used on 850 series.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Optimize speed to the maximum</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Achieve incredible read / write performance, help you complete your daily tasks quickly with&nbsp;Samsung&#39;s&nbsp;<strong>Intelligent TurboWrite</strong>&nbsp;technology&nbsp;.&nbsp;With this new technology, Samsung 860 EVO performance is increased 1.9 times compared to the 840 Evo.&nbsp;Samsung 860 EVO SSD hard drive offers top class read speed (550MB / s) and write (520Mb / s).&nbsp;Also, optimize random performance IOPs up to 98k.</p>\r\n', 1, 250),
(69, 'SSD Samsung 860 Evo 500GB 2.5-Inch SATA III MZ-76E500BW', 70, 40, '860-evo-2-5-inch-01.jpg,860-evo-2-5-inch-02-2809749d-cf4b-43a0-b0be-ce2e49615337.jpg,860-evo-2-5-inch-04-cac55405-ab76-4575-8f40-6d62ee1d016e.jpg', 3, 3, '<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		SSD standard: M.2 2280 SATA III\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Read speed: 550 MB / s\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Recording speed: 520 MB / s\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Warranty 5 years 1 exchange 1.\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p><strong>Hard drive&nbsp;Samsung SSD 860 line drives to be upgraded from the current 850 EVO reputation and best-selling worldwide, is the best choice for gamers in both price and performance is confirmed and detailed evaluation Details by the world&#39;s leading technology magazines such as Cnet, thessdreview, the PC World.&nbsp;TweakTown ..</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Samsung 64-Layer 3D V-NAND Technology</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Samsung Technology 64-Samsung&#39;s 3D Layer V-NAND is a breakthrough in Flash memory architecture by increasing the density, performance, and limit of endurance of conventional flat NAND architecture.&nbsp;The Samsung 3D V-NAND technology arranges 64 layers of longitudinal Cell cells which increases the Cell density higher and performs twice as well as the 32-Layer technology used on 850 series.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Samsung 64-Layer 3D V-NAND Technology</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Samsung Technology 64-Samsung&#39;s 3D Layer V-NAND is a breakthrough in Flash memory architecture by increasing the density, performance, and limit of endurance of conventional flat NAND architecture.&nbsp;The Samsung 3D V-NAND technology arranges 64 layers of longitudinal Cell cells which increases the Cell density higher and performs twice as well as the 32-Layer technology used on 850 series.</p>\r\n', 1, 500),
(70, 'SSD Samsung 860 Pro Series 512GB MZ-76P512BW', 85, 20, '860-evo-2-5-inch-04-cac55405-ab76-4575-8f40-6d62ee1d016e.jpg,860-pro-2-5-inch-01-0956682b-6b98-42ab-abdb-eb6d42b83203.jpg,860-pro-2-5-inch-02-8b68e50a-2cef-49ea-8747-64f379bc99bd.jpg', 3, 3, '<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		SSD standard: M.2 2280 SATA III\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Read speed: 550 MB / s\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Recording speed: 520 MB / s\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Warranty 5 years 1 exchange 1.\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p><strong>Samsung 64-Layer 3D V-NAND Technology</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Samsung Technology 64-Samsung&#39;s 3D Layer V-NAND is a breakthrough in Flash memory architecture by increasing the density, performance, and limit of endurance of conventional flat NAND architecture.&nbsp;The Samsung 3D V-NAND technology arranges 64 layers of longitudinal Cell cells which increases the Cell density higher and performs twice as well as the 32-Layer technology used on 850 series.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Optimize speed to the maximum</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Achieve incredible read / write performance, help you complete your daily tasks quickly with&nbsp;Samsung&#39;s&nbsp;<strong>Intelligent TurboWrite</strong>&nbsp;technology&nbsp;.&nbsp;With this new technology, Samsung 860 EVO performance is increased 1.9 times compared to the 840 Evo.&nbsp;Samsung 860 EVO SSD hard drive offers top class read speed (550MB / s) and write (520Mb / s).&nbsp;Also, optimize random performance IOPs up to 98k.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>RAPID Mode</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Samsung&#39;s&nbsp;<strong>Magician</strong>&nbsp;software&nbsp;is equipped with&nbsp;<strong>RAPID Mode</strong>&nbsp;.&nbsp;When activated, it will increase the performance of Samsung 860 Evo SSD many times by using free RAM PC memory as a high-speed cache.&nbsp;The latest version of Samsung Magician supports up to 4 GB of Cache memory on a 16GB DRAM system.</p>\r\n', 1, 512);
