(71, 'SSD Samsung 970 EVO PCIe NVMe V-NAND M.2 2280 250GB MZ-V7E250BW', 99, 35, '970-evo-250-01.jpg', 3, 3, '<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Standard SSD: M.2 NVMe Gen3 x4\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Read speed: 3400 MB / s\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Recording speed: 1500 MB / s\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		<strong>Warranty 5 years 1 exchange 1.</strong>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p><strong>Standard connection of the latest NVMe PCIe Gen3 x4</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>With the change from Polaris Controller used for the 960 Evo generation, Samsung 970 EVO PCIe NVMe M.2 2280 V-NAND hard drive equipped with the latest Phoenix Controller for better support for Games processes and arrangement streamlined graphics intensive workflows, accompanied by intelligent TurboWrite technology, for sequential read / write speeds of up to 3,500 MB / s and 2,500 MB / s, up to 32% faster than the previous generation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Capacity up to 2TB</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Samsung 970 EVO PCIe NVMe M.2 2280 V-NAND hard drive with the latest NVMe SSD technology will now deliver a tremendous 2TB capacity on the compact M.2 2280 standard design, which helps you maximize your capabilities. Storage capacity and save space in your computer.&nbsp;In addition, Samsung SSD hard drive 970 EVO PCIe NVMe M.2 2280 V-NAND also has capacities ranging from 250GB, 500GB, 1TB and 2TB to meet all your capacity needs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Dynamic Thermal Guard - Controller covered with Nickel</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Dynamic Thermal Guard, a technology that automatically adjusts the temperature of a drive equipped with an SSD Samsung 970 EVO PCIe NVMe M.2 2280 V-NAND, when the drive is so hot that it will automatically drop. performance or shutdown to minimize the risk of data loss.&nbsp;Accompanied by a new cooling solution from Samsung that is nickel-coated controller, which helps controller cool the best possible heat.</p>\r\n', 0, 250),
(72, 'SSD Samsung 970 Pro PCIe NVMe V-NAND M.2 2280 1TB MZ-V7P1T0BW', 199, 45, '970-pro-00-4afb88e2-0e6d-4973-8e28-27ac0bb848f4.jpg', 3, 3, '<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Standard SSD: M.2 NVMe Gen3 x4\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Read speed: 3500 MB / s\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Recording speed: 2700 MB / s\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Warranty: 3 years\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h2>The SSD that goes beyond</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Experience the best. For intensive workloads on PCs and workstations, the 970 PRO delivers ultimate performance powered by Samsung&#39;s NVMe SSD leadership. The latest V-NAND technology and new Phoenix controller in a compact M.2 (2280) form factor meets the&nbsp; needs of the most demanding tech enthusiasts and professionals.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Fearless Performance</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Performance that puts you in command. The 970 PRO combines the next-gen PCIe Gen 3x4 NVMe interface with the latest V-NAND technology and a newly enhanced Phoenix controller to achieve fearless read/write speeds up to 3,500/2,700 MB/s*, approximately 30 percent faster than the previous generation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Dynamic Thermal Guard - Controller covered with Nickel</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Dynamic Thermal Guard, a technology that automatically adjusts the temperature of a drive equipped with an SSD Samsung 970 EVO PCIe NVMe M.2 2280 V-NAND, when the drive is so hot that it will automatically drop. performance or shutdown to minimize the risk of data loss.&nbsp;Accompanied by a new cooling solution from Samsung that is nickel-coated controller, which helps controller cool the best possible heat.</p>\r\n', 1, 1000),
(73, 'SSD Samsung NVMe PM961 M.2 PCIe Gen3 x4 1TB MZ-VLW1T00', 360, 16, 'pm961-01-9490ef48-d36b-4725-a5ef-ddc7b72ffb28.jpg,pm961-02-ecb24677-1a22-41f6-b01b-8740e6700479.jpg', 3, 3, '<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Standard SSD: M.2 NVMe Gen3 x4\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Read speed: 3500 MB / s\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Recording speed: 2700 MB / s\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Warranty: 3 years\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h2>Unparalleled Reliability</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Achieve a new level of drive confidence. Samsung&rsquo;s advanced nickel-coated controller and heat spreader on the 970 PRO enable superior heat dissipation. The Dynamic Thermal Guard automatically monitors and maintains optimal operating temperatures to minimize performance drops.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Exceptional Endurance</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Get the ultimate sustainable performance. The 970 PRO delivers up to 1,200 TBW* with a 5-year limited warranty, achieving 50 percent greater endurance than the previous generation, all powered by the latest V-NAND technology.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>* TBW: Terabytes Written<br />\r\n<br />\r\n* Warrantied TBW for 970 PRO: 600 TBW for 512GB model, 1,200 TBW for 1TB model.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n* 5-years or TBW, whichever comes first. For more information on the warranty, please find the enclosed warranty statement in the package.</p>\r\n', 1, 1000),
(74, 'SSD Western Digital Black PCIe Gen3 x4 NVMe M.2 500GB WDS500G2X0C 2018', 180, 39, 'wdblack-pcie-2018-01-4ed1b61b-ee88-4163-8fae-f963db30ef60.jpg', 3, 1, '<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Standard SSD: M.2 NVMe Gen3 x4\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Read speed: 3400 MB / s\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Recording speed: 2500 MB / s\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Genuine warranty January 60 exchange 1\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p><a href=\"https://www.memoryzone.com.vn/ssd-western-digital-black-pcie-gen3-x4-nvme-m-2-500gb-wds500g2x0c-2018\"><strong>Black PCIe Gen3 x4 NVMe M.2 2018 SSD hard drive</strong></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Compact - reliable - high performance</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>With continuous read and write speeds of up to 3400 MB / s and 2800MB / s, Black PCIe Western Digital SSD Gen3 x4 NVMe M.2 2018 is equipped with the latest technologies and platforms with 3D technology - NAND 64 Layer will maximize performance to help your PC meet the needs of the most demanding hardware, VR applications and software.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Sequential read speeds of up to 3400 MB / s.</li>\r\n	<li>Thermal and energy management and optimization to help maintain the highest performance.</li>\r\n	<li>1.75M MTTF for long-term reliability.</li>\r\n	<li>Warranty up to 5 years.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Extremely high speed</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>With sequential read speeds of up to 3400 MB / s, seven times faster than SATA III SSDs, Black PCIe Western Digital SSD hard drives Gen3 x4 NVMe M.2 2018 handle even the required computing tasks The most heavy resource.&nbsp;Launch your system quickly, load super fast games and easily multitask with Black Digital Black PCIe Gen3 x4 NVMe M.2 2018 SSDs.</p>\r\n', 1, 500),
