(115, 'Seagate Backup Plus Slim 2TB', 99, 14, 'seagate-backup-plus-slim-black-f40ff6dd-b9d4-44b3-9ca7-a6319678e14c.jpg,seagate-backup-plus-slim-blue.jpg,seagate-backup-plus-slim-gold.jpg', 8, 16, '<p>\r\n	Type: External portable hard drive<br>\r\n	Capacity: 2 TB<br>\r\n	Read speed: USB 3.0<br>\r\n	Warranty: 3 Years\r\n</p>\r\n', '<p><img alt=\"Expansion Portable Hard Drives\" src=\"https://www.seagate.com/files/www-content/product-content/expansion-fam/expansion-portable/_shared/images/highlight-nexpansion-portable-1-570x296.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>The easy-to-use storage solution</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Expansion portable hard drive can be installed easily by plugging in a single USB cord. You can start saving your digital files to this external hard drive within seconds of removing it from the box.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Expansion Portable Hard Drives\" src=\"https://www.seagate.com/files/www-content/product-content/expansion-fam/expansion-portable/_shared/images/highlight-expansion-portable-2-570x216.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Instantly adds storage capacity</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Digital photos, videos and music files can tax your computer&rsquo;s storage, causing performance to decline as its internal hard drive fills to capacity. The Expansion portable hard drive features a range of capacities, with the 1TB model offering enough data storage for:</p>\r\n', 1, 2000),
(116, 'Seagate Backup Plus Ultra Slim 1TB', 60, 22, 'ultraslim-01.jpg,ultraslim-02.jpg,ultraslim-04.jpg', 8, 16, 'Category: Hard Drive External\r\nCapacity: 1 TB\r\nRead speed: USB 3.0\r\nWarranty: 3 Years', '<h2>Instantly adds storage capacity</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Digital photos, videos and music files can tax your computer&rsquo;s storage, causing performance to decline as its internal hard drive fills to capacity. The Expansion portable hard drive features a range of capacities, with the 1TB model offering enough data storage for:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Up to 1,000 hours of digital video</li>\r\n	<li>Up to 250 two-hour DVD films</li>\r\n	<li>Up to 320,000 digital photos</li>\r\n	<li>Up to 16,660 hours of digital music</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 1, 1000),
(117, 'Seagate Backup Plus Ultra Slim 2TB', 82, 32, 'ultraslim-01.jpg,ultraslim-02.jpg,ultraslim-04.jpg', 8, 16, '<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Category: Mobile Hard Drive External\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Capacity: 2 TB\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Read speed: USB 3.0\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Warranty: 3 Years\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h2>Installs in seconds</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Seagate&reg; Expansion&trade; portable hard drive features make it incredibly easy to use this drive right from the box.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Simply plug the included USB cable into your computer &ndash; no external power supply is needed.</li>\r\n	<li>The drive is automatically recognised by the Windows operating system &ndash; no software to install and nothing to configure.</li>\r\n	<li>Drag and drop to save files to the Expansion portable drive.</li>\r\n	<li>Built-in power management automatically ensures energy-efficient operation</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 1, 2000),
(118, 'Seagate Wireless Plus 1TB USB 3.0', 99, 10, 'seagate-wireless-plus-01.jpg,seagate-wireless-plus-02.jpg,seagate-wireless-plus-04.jpg', 8, 16, '<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Category: Mobile Hard Drive External\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Capacity: 2 TB\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Read speed: USB 3.0\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Warranty: 3 Years\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p>Available in four capacities of 500GB, 1TB, 2TB and 4TB, the drive currently costs just $60, $61, $89 and $199, respectively. (Note that the newly-released 4TB drive&#39;s street price is expected to be lower.) And in my testing, the new drive proved to be one of the fastest of its type. What&#39;s more, the drive includes helpful backup software for your local data, social-media content, and even mobile devices.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Note that the 4TB is largest capacity for a compact single-volume portable drive, rivaling many desktop drives that are a few time larger in physical size. The drive is ideal for those wanting to carry their entire music, home video library with them on the go.</p>\r\n', 1, 1000),
(119, 'Seagate Wireless Plus 2TB USB 3.0', 149, 12, 'seagate-wireless-plus-01.jpg,seagate-wireless-plus-02.jpg,seagate-wireless-plus-04.jpg', 8, 16, '<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Type: External portable hard drive\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Capacity: 2 TB\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Read speed: USB 3.0\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Warranty: 3 Years\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<h3><strong>Simple add-on storage that goes with you</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The Seagate Expansion Portable hard drive offers an easy-to-use solution when you need to instantly add storage to your computer and take files on the go.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Drag and drop file saving, right out of the box</li>\r\n	<li>USB powered</li>\r\n	<li>Fast data transfer with USB 3.0 connectivity</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>The easy-to-use storage solution</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Expansion portable hard drive can be installed easily by plugging in a single USB cord. You can start saving your digital files to this external hard drive within seconds of removing it from the box.</p>\r\n', 1, 2000),
(120, 'SSHD SEAGATE FIRECUDA 1TB SATA 6GBPS128MB CACHE 5400RPM 2.5&#8243;', 99, 10, 'FIRECUDA-1TB-2.5-1.jpg,FIRECUDA-1TB-2.5-3.jpg,FIRECUDA-1TB-2.5-4.jpg', 8, 16, '<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Manufacturer: Seagate\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Capacity: 500 GB\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Cache: 128MB\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Data transfer rate: 140 MB / sec\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		NAND technology: 4 GB\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Size: 2.5 &#39;&#39;\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p><strong>Seagate SSHD internal hard drive for laptop</strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A unique combination of traditional HDD and SSD with a compact 2.5-inch design, ultra-light hard drive weight does not increase the weight of your computer.&nbsp;500 GB capacity enough to meet your storage needs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>More information</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>The unique blend of disc recording technology of traditional HDD hard drives and flash chip recording technology of SSDs helps your device become more powerful and amazing data processing speed.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Seagate FireCuda hard drive 2.5 &quot;in</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;addition to your drive capacity also has an additional&nbsp;<strong>32 GB</strong>&nbsp;of NAND FLash form capacity to increase the performance up to 4 to 5 times that of normal, standard SATA 6Gb / s hard drives.</li>\r\n	<li>Although the design is quite compact, but you do not need to worry about stability and its processing&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp;</strong>speed still has amazing data processing speed on laptops and high stability is no different from a hard drive 3.5 inches on a desktop computer.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Seagate Firecuda 2.5 &quot;</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;is a reliable choice for gamers and users who require very high data processing speed.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 1, 1000),
