(124, 'Western Digital My Passport 2TB WDBYNN0010B', 99, 35, 'western-digital-my-passport-1tb-new-2017-black.jpg,western-digital-my-passport-1tb-new-2017-red.jpg,western-digital-my-passport-1tb-new-2017-yellow-3.jpg', 8, 1, '<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Type: External portable hard drive\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Capacity: 2 TB\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		Read speed: USB 3.0 5 Gbps\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n		3 year warranty\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<p><a href=\"https://www.memoryzone.com.vn/o-cung-di-dong-western-digital-passport-2tb-new-2017\"><strong>Western Digital My Passport mobile hard drive</strong></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Western Digital My Passport mobile hard drive with worldwide reputation for reliability gives you peace of mind when storing your important data.&nbsp;New design with many colors for your style, compact size makes it easy to bring your precious content everywhere you want.&nbsp;<em><strong>Outstanding features:</strong></em>&nbsp;- Automatically backup with WD Backup Software included - Support password protection with hardware encryption - Easy to use - Many colors for you to choose - Extreme quality good with WD standard - Maximum capacity up to 4TB - USB 3.0 communication standard;&nbsp;USB 2.0 backwards compatible</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Data protection with password</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>With 256-bit AES hardware encryption integrated with WD Security software helps keep your data private and secure.&nbsp;Easily recover passwords quickly in case you forget your password.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Easy to use</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Western Digital My Passport portable hard drive is easy to use, just plug it into your computer and don&#39;t need any software or drivers.&nbsp;In addition, the Western Digital My Passport portable hard drive comes with all the software you need to help protect all your data, including WD Backup Software and WD Security software.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 1, 2000),
